transcript:

Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan, hello.
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan, hello.
Executive: Haan ji sir, mai IndiaMART se baat kar rahi hu.
Customer: Haan, bataiye madam.
Executive: Ji bataiye sir.
Customer: Aap hi se baat hui thi abhi call aaya tha aapka.
Executive: Haan, maine aapko call kiya tha. Aapne aapka feedback aaya hai hamare paas mein.
Customer: Thik hai madam, thank you. Ji. To usi feedback pe, ji?
Customer: Koi baat nahi madam, thik hai.
Executive: Nahi aapke feedback pe discussion karna hai.
